%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System

    User->>Claude: /create-frontend-docs [--force-rerun] [--only <area>]

    note over Claude,FS: Preflight
    Claude->>Claude: START_TS = date +%s
    Claude->>FS: Check .claude/ exists
    FS-->>Claude: ok / missing
    Claude->>FS: Read .claude/state/frontend-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: JSON / not found

    alt JSON not found
        Claude->>User: No analysis JSON found.<br/>Run /analyze-frontend first.
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    alt schema_version mismatch
        Claude->>User: Schema mismatch (expected 1.1, got <ver>).<br/>Re-run /analyze-frontend to regenerate.
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    opt JSON older than 30 days
        Claude->>User: Analysis is stale (generated X days ago).<br/>[1] Continue with stale data<br/>[2] Re-run /analyze-frontend first (recommended)<br/>[3] Cancel
        User-->>Claude: Choice
    end

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Assemble + write artefacts
    Claude->>Claude: TodoWrite — create checklist before starting:<br/>☐ Assemble template sections from JSON<br/>☐ Write reference-component-creation-template.md<br/>☐ Write frontend-design-system.md<br/>☐ Write frontend-components.md<br/>☐ Write reference-architecture-frontend.md<br/>☐ Write reference-component-inventory.md<br/>☐ Write frontend-data-flow.mmd<br/>☐ Write sequences/features/<pattern>.mmd<br/>☐ Update CLAUDE.md ## Architecture

    Claude->>Claude: Assemble template from JSON sections<br/>(tech_stack → framework_idioms → design_system →<br/>component_inventory → data_flow → feature_flows)
    Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Assemble template sections from JSON

    Claude->>User: Template ready (~N lines).<br/>Artefacts to write: N files.<br/>[1] Write all  (default)<br/>[2] Write only template<br/>[3] Choose which to skip<br/>[4] Cancel
    User-->>Claude: Choice

    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/reference-component-creation-template.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write reference-component-creation-template.md

    opt design_system section non-null
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/rules/frontend-design-system.md
        FS-->>Claude: OK
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write frontend-design-system.md
    end
    opt component_inventory section non-null
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/rules/frontend-components.md +<br/>.claude/docs/reference-component-inventory.md
        FS-->>Claude: OK
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write frontend-components.md
    end
    opt architecture + tech_stack non-null
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/reference-architecture-frontend.md
        FS-->>Claude: OK
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write reference-architecture-frontend.md
    end
    opt data_flow.primary_flow_mermaid non-null
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/frontend-data-flow.mmd
        FS-->>Claude: OK
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write frontend-data-flow.mmd
    end
    opt feature_flows non-null
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/features/<pattern>.mmd
        FS-->>Claude: OK
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ Write sequences/features/<pattern>.mmd
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Update root CLAUDE.md Architecture section
    Claude->>FS: Read root CLAUDE.md
    FS-->>Claude: content
    Claude->>Claude: Locate ## Architecture → ### Frontend.<br/>Replace-in-place or append cross-refs.
